dublin_core.dcvalue: Telehealth is a method to expand the reach of clinical care for PTSD treatment However those with limited prior exposure to telehealth or limited confidence using telehealth may have poorer treatment response The present study examined familiarity with telehealth as a moderator of treatment response for a behavioral treatment delivered via telehealth
